N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 45.5 - Prohibited movement

State Regulations

No person shall move or cause to be moved live poultry
except in compliance with this Part. No person shall receive or accept for
delivery live poultry in violation of this Part. Notes
